factors.name: Measurement
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the values to use in the computation.

Example:

* log transformed and ComBat Corrected S100
* VSN transformed S100

factors.description:

factors.description:

* Test Condition
* Treatment off chip

factors.description:

Example:
* Barcode and Row
* Barcode and Array
